        "The Verb BOIRE (Present Tense)",
        "1. Conjugation:",
        "   - Je bois (I drink)",
        "   - Tu bois (You drink)",
        "   - Il/Elle boit (He/She drinks)",
        "   - Nous buvons (We drink)",
        "   - Vous buvez (You all drink)",
        "   - Ils/Elles boivent (They drink)",
        "2. Examples:",
        "   - Je bois de l'eau. (I drink water.)",
        "   - Il boit du café. (He drinks coffee.)",
        "   - Nous buvons du lait. (We drink milk.)",
        "3. Note:",
        "   - 'Boire' is an irregular verb. Memorize the 'nous/vous' forms (buvons/buvez)."
